Creapiing stood beneath the Dragon of Hate, the sacred spot of their ceremonies and meetings. The Triad had taken their places to complete the triangle. She felt the power of the connection flow through them and engage the ancient power of the dragon. Surely Innoruuk watched over this meeting as he did all them, Innoruuk had never forsaken his chosen.<br>
<br>
Looking about, Creapiing caught the eye of the one called the *general*. He stood with the military dignity of one who would never look relaxed. In fact, she doubted he even relaxed in the baths. <br>
<br>
Something looked a bit different in his eye and she allowed her mind to probe deeper into his thoughts. A dark smile crossed her face. This one had come to the Violent Harvest as a military leader, but now, now he had the fervor of the prophets visions upon him. She nodded to the General, an acknowledgement that she welcomed him into the spiritual *family* that was the Violent Harvest.<br>
<br>
And with that act, the dragon of hate pulsed energy thoughout her body and the body of all in the Triad and they emanated energy and sense of purpose. Carefully she pulled forth the sacred chalice and set it upon its dark cloth, *who here requests a ceremony today?* she asked with a dark smile and deep tone.  <br>
